[SN]TITLE[SN]
Police name man, 97, killed by car in Knighton, Powys

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
An elderly man who died after being hit by a car in Powys has been named by police as 97-year-old Richard Wood.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The A4113 Bridge Street in Knighton was closed following the incident on Thursday at about 10:25 GMT.
The Wales Air Ambulance and road ambulances were called to the scene between Larkey Lane and Presteigne Road.
Police urged anyone who saw the incident to come forward.
